    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm working as a corporate wellness coach for a few firms and I've been asked to put together some guidance for our execs. Can you give me some tips on grooming and general appearance that help employees project a sense of authority and high-level professionalism during big boardroom meetings? Just looking for the standard \"look\" that works best in those settings.",
