      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "For boardroom authority, a sharp, tailored suit in conservative colors like navy or charcoal is the standard. Ensure your grooming is impeccable, meaning hair is neatly styled and nails are clean, projecting meticulous attention to detail. High-quality, polished leather shoes are essential, as they complete the look of competence and seriousness. Overall, the goal is to appear polished, controlled, and effortlessly powerful.",
